        CFI ResourceParts SP SPH, SPL
        CFI ResourceParts Y R29, R28
        CFI EndNames cfiNames0
        
        CFI Common cfiCommon0 Using cfiNames0
        CFI CodeAlign 1
        CFI DataAlign 1
        CFI ReturnAddress ?Ret CODE
        CFI CFA_Y Y+0
        CFI CFA_SP SP+2
